<paragraph id="IFRS17_BC68" base="F55751227"><paranum>BC68</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 17"/><data name="paranum" value="BC68"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS17_P5918">The following aspects of the definition of an insurance contract are discussed below:</p><ol id="IFRS17_L0452" base="F55751229" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS17_P5919" base="F55751230">the definition of a contract (see <xref id="IFRS17_X1470" base="F59367527" href="IFRS17_gBC69-BC70.dita#IFRS17_gBC69-BC70/IFRS17_gBC69-BC70_TI">paragraphs BC69&#x2013;BC70</xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS17_P5920" base="F55751232">the insurance risk (see <xref id="IFRS17_X1471" base="F59367528" href="IFRS17_gBC71-BC72.dita#IFRS17_gBC71-BC72/IFRS17_gBC71-BC72_TI">paragraphs BC71&#x2013;BC72</xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p id="IFRS17_P5921" base="F55751234">the insurable interest (see <xref id="IFRS17_X1472" base="F59367529" href="IFRS17_gBC73-BC75.dita#IFRS17_gBC73-BC75/IFRS17_gBC73-BC75_TI">paragraphs BC73&#x2013;BC75</xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(d)</li_value> <p id="IFRS17_P5922" base="F55751236">the quantity of insurance risk (see <xref id="IFRS17_X1473" base="F59367530" href="IFRS17_gBC76-BC80.dita#IFRS17_gBC76-BC80/IFRS17_gBC76-BC80_TI">paragraphs BC76&#x2013;BC80</xref>); and</p></li><li><li_value>(e)</li_value> <p id="IFRS17_P5923" base="F55751238">the expiry of insurance-contingent rights and obligations (see <xref id="IFRS17_X1474" base="F59367531" href="IFRS17_gBC81-BC81.dita#IFRS17_gBC81-BC81/IFRS17_gBC81-BC81_TI">paragraph BC81</xref>).</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>